items.headline: Join the Godafther VG Fanon Wiki!
items.desc:
This wiki is about fan fiction related to the Godfather series of video games published by Electronic Arts. 

The most recent, Godfather II, takes place on the eve of the Cuban revolution where a major mob meeting in Havana takes a bloody turn. The Don of your family is killed, and you must take the reigns and lead your battered organization.
